{"tid":1898060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[財案] 比四億五千萬元讓律政司推廣香港社會對法治概念的認識及實踐","createTime":"2020-02-26T03:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T03:53:03.000Z","uid":85406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4bad78289eb5c13c979e32a155469af613ca1382","tid":1898060,"uid":85406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:45:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.budget.gov.hk/2020/chi/budget18.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.gov.hk%2F2020%2Fchi%2Fbudget18.html&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=c2f7c71c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.budget.gov.hk/2020/chi/budget18.html</a><br />\n<br />\n專業服務<br />\n<br />\n82. 香港專業服務業憑藉優秀的人才和豐富的國際經驗，支援香港不同行業的發展，鞏固香港作為國際金融和商貿中心的地位。我們會繼續促進業界拓展國際和內地市場，並爭取以「先行先試」方式推動香港專業服務在大灣區的發展。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n83. 尊重法治、司法獨立，是香港賴以成功的基石之一。我會預留約四億五千萬元，讓律政司推行「願景2030&mdash;聚焦法治」計劃，加深香港社會對法治概念的認識及實踐。</span>"},{"pid":"2aaaf958ea8fe2e13d8300b8ee8874bbecb9cdaa","tid":1898060,"uid":85406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T03:53:03.000Z","msg":"推"}]}